cho mi ch . Nhn thy iu ny nn lun vn s trnh by v ti "Tm

1 Tng quan
1.1 ng lc nghin cu
Tm tt vn bn l mt bi ton nghin cu quan trng trong lnh vc x l ngn
ng t nhin, c tnh ng dng rt ln trong i sng hin i. Tm tt vn bn
gip con ngi nhanh chng tip cn cc chnh, ni dung ni bt ca ti liu m
khng cn phi c ton b, t tit kim c nhiu thi gian, cng sc. ng
dng ca tm tt vn bn th hin trong nhiu lnh vc thc t :
Lnh vc bo ch: Trn cc trang bo in t, ta c th hin th cc on tm
tt ca bi bo bn ngoi, ngi c c th nm c ni dung chnh
v quyt nh s bm vo c chi tit bi bo hay khng. iu ny to rt
nhiu thun tin cho c gi tm c ni dung ph hp vi mnh.
Lnh vc phn tch: Ta lun cn bn tm tt cho tng ch , lnh vc trong
mt bn bo co ln, gip ngi c c mt ci nhn tng qut, nhanh chng
v cc vn trnh by trong .
Lnh vc gio dc: Trong cc tc phm vn hc, hay lch s c th to ra cc
bn tm lc ni dung, iu ny gip ch cho hc sinh nm c cc ni dung
chnh ca bi hc, tip thu kin thc d dng hn.
Vi mt m hnh tm tt, s em li rt nhiu li ch:
Kh nng nm bt thng tin: ta ch phi c mt vn bn ngn, sc tch v
ni dung ng nhin s gip ta nh v nm c cc chnh nhanh hn.
Kh nng tm kim: Thay v phi tm v c qua cc vn bn di v nhiu ,
h thng c th da vo cc bn tm tt ngn hn tm kim cc vn bn
ny, gip tit kim ti nguyn v thi gian.
Nhng iu nu trn th hin gi tr v tnh ng dng ln ca tm tt vn
bn trong thc t. Tuy nhin vn cn rt nhiu thch thc nh phi x l mt vn
bn c di ln, bn tm tt sinh ra cha ni dung chnh, v b kh c do sinh
sai ng ngha, ng php. Nhng kh khn ny t ra rt nhiu vn cn nghin
cu, gii quyt cho bi ton tm tt vn bn.

1.2 Mc tiu nghin cu
Khi c mt vn bn hay ti liu, hnh vi ph bin ca con ngi l c lt
chn lc cc thng tin quan trng ng ch hay phn thng tin m mnh quan
tm. Trong mt ti liu c th bao gm nhiu phn ni dung khc nhau v cc ch
khc nhau, m c th mi ngi quan tm n mt ch trong . iu
ny sinh ra vn ta cn phi to ra nhiu bn tm tt cho tng ch trong vn
bn, gip bn tm tt tp trung, th hin nhng phn thng tin ring bit.
Xut pht t nhng vn , lun vn tp trung nghin cu bi ton sinh cc
tm tt theo tng ch ca mt vn bn. Thay v ch c mt bn tm tt duy
nht, ta s thu c cc bn tm tt theo tng ch ring bit vi ni dung chuyn
bit. iu ny gip ngi c d dng tp trung vo phn thng tin m mnh quan
tm.
Lun vn s hng ti kt hp c m hnh tm tt trch rt v tm tt tm lc
theo ch nhm nng cao cht lng ca cc bn tm tt.
1.3 ng gp nghin cu
Lun vn tp trung vo cc nhim v chnh:
Xy dng tp d liu bao gm cc vn bn v cc tm tt ring bit theo cc
ch . Do s hn ch ca d liu, ta phi t to tp d liu ph hp vi bi
ton ra t cc tp d liu cng b c sn.
Xy dng m hnh tm tt theo cc ch bng s kt hp ca tm tt trch
rt v tm tt tm lc. Thc hin hun luyn m hnh theo cc chin lc
khc nhau nhm tm ra phng php nng cao cht lng cc bn tm tt.
1.4 Cu trc lun vn
Phn m u ca lun vn trnh by v ng lc, mc tiu nghin cu ca
lun vn.
Phn th hai s l cc khi nim c bn, c s l thuyt v hc my, mng
hc su v l thuyt x l ngn ng t nhin. Phn ny tp trung vo cc
kin thc c bn, m hnh nn tng phc v cho cc phn tip theo. Trong
mc ny ta cn trnh by v cc nghin cu lin quan n bi ton tm tt
vi hai phng php tm tt chnh: trch rt v tm lc.
Phn th ba trnh by v cc m hnh gii quyt bi ton sinh nhiu tm tt
theo cc ch , m hnh s l s kt hp ca c m hnh tm tt trch rt v
m hnh tm tt tm lc.
10
Phn th t a ra cc cch thc sinh ra b d liu a tm tt theo tng ch
cho mi mt vn bn, phc v mc tiu ca nghin cu t cc b d liu
c sn c cng b. Thc hin cc thc nghim trn tp d liu ta sinh
ra, t so snh v a ra nh gi, nhn xt s hiu qu ca tng m hnh.
Phn th nm ta s tng kt a ra kt lun ca nghin cu, nhn xt v
nghin cu v m ra cc hng pht trin tng lai cho bi ton.

2 C s l thuyt
2.1 Mng neural nhn to
Mng neural nhn to (Artificial Neural Network - ANN) [31] l m hnh x l
thng tin m phng da trn hot ng ca no con ngi, bao gm s lng ln
cc neural c lin kt qua nhiu lp x l thng tin. ANN ging nh b no
con ngi, n c cp nhp, hc hi nh vo vic hun luyn, c kh nng lu gi
nhng hiu bit v s dng trong vic x l cc d liu cha bit sau ny. Cu trc
ca ANN gip h tr vic x l thng tin song song mc cao, c kh nng hc
hi, ghi nh, v tng qut t d liu hc bng cch t iu chnh cc gi tr trng
s ca cc lin kt gia cc neural. Chc nng ca mt mng ANN xc nh bi:
kin trc ca mng neural, c tnh vo ra ca mi neural, chin lc hun luyn
v d liu hc.
Cu trc ca mt n-ron nhn to bao gm:
- D liu vo (Inputs): Mi Input ng vi 1 thuc tnh ca d liu.
- Kt qu (Outputs): Kt qu ca mt ANN l mt gii php cho bi ton, c
th l mt phn b xc sut, . . . .
- Trng s lin kt: n th hin mc quan trng ca d liu u vo i vi
qu trnh x l, lan truyn gia cc lp.
- Hm tng (Summation Function): L hm tch hp ca cc tn hiu u vo.
- Hm truyn hay hm kch hot (Active function): Hm ny c dng gii
hn phm vi u ra ca mi n-ron. Thng thng, phm vi u ra ca mi n-ron
c gii hn trong on [0,1] hoc [1,1]. C rt nhiu loi hm truyn, vic la
chn hm no ty thuc vo tng yu cu ca bi ton.

2.2 Kin trc mng neural c bn [2]
Hnh 2: Kin trc mng neural c bn [2]
Mng neural l s kt hp ca nhiu tng, bao gm ba tng chnh:
+ Tng u vo (input layer): L tng u tin, nhn cc d liu u vo
ca mng.
+ Tng u ra (output layer): L tng cui cng, th hin u ra ca mng.
+ Tng n (hidden layer): Tng nm gia tng vo v ra ca mng, biu th
cho s lin kt gia cc neural trong mng.
mi tng trong mng, s lng neural c th khc nhau ph thuc vo bi
ton c th. Cc neural trong cc tng c s lin kt vi nhau. Trong trng hp
mi neural ca mt tng lin kt vi cc neural ca tng k tip ta s c mng kt
ni y (full-connected network) [36].
13
Ti u ra ca mi neural trong cc tng n, chng u i qua mt hm phi
tuyn gi l hm tc ng (activation function) v c s dng lm u vo cho
tng tip theo. Ta s tm hiu cc hm tc ng hay s dng trong mng neural.

Rouge-L l o da vo cc chui con di nht khi so snh hai bn tm tt
vi nhau (Longest Common Subsequence). Tuy nhin khc vi n-gram, chui con

trong cu t ra ph hp nh gi hiu qu cu tm tt. im mnh na ca
Rouge-L l gip ta khng phi nh ngha trc gi tr ca n-gram, khi n xt n
cc chui cc gram di nht.
